---
title: Sticky Honey Soy Salmon Rice Bowl with Sesame Sugar Snap Peas and Sriracha Drizzle
description: This Sticky Honey Soy Salmon Rice Bowl is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
